.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-LISTFORWARDS-FEE-TOTAL-MONTHLY" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-listforwards-fee-total-monthly \- FEAT-2871 node-listforwards-fee-total-monthly
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-listforwards-fee-total-monthly
.SH DESCRIPTION
Total forward fees earned this calendar month for the local node (FEAT-2871).
.PP
Queries settled forwards via lightning-cli listforwards and sums fee_msat for
entries whose resolved_time falls within the current UTC calendar month.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
